snippet.title: Epic Skater 2 - On the App Store and Google Play
snippet.description:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yourdailyfill.epicskater2
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/epic-skater-2/id1160596089
https://www.epicskater.com for more info.

Epic Skater 2 is now available worldwide and FREE on Google Play and the App Store.
